    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver or a great project car for someone looking to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with various scuffs and small dings around the body. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, but the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may require some upcoming maintenance for peak performance. It's an honest car at an affordable price point.",
