    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute beauty! It is in truly breathtaking condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is sparkling, the interior still has that fresh new-car smell, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. It's totally ready for its next adventure, so come take a look before someone else snaps up this gem! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
