    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen remains mechanically superlative, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The naturally aspirated induction through individual throttle bodies provides instantaneous throttle response, sent through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a lock-up limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping profiles with fresh bushings and mounts, ensuring the chassis delivers the communicative feedback this platform is renowned for. Cosmetically flawless with original paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
